<h1 style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:19.05pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-13.45pt;font-size:16px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><strong>3. TRATAMIENTO DE DATOS&nbsp;SENSIBLES</strong></h1>
